extendedInfo.description: WP7 Blue is a free black/blue theme for GOSMS Pro inspired in the slick and mimalistic Windows Phone 7 interface.All you need is install GOSMS Pro for free and then this theme, also FREE!Instructions:1. Download GOSMS Pro from the Android Market for free.2. Download WP7 theme from here.3. Go to GOSMS > Settings > Theme > WP7 Blue.4. Enjoy!Keywords: GO SMS, WP7, WP8 theme, Windows Phone 7 theme, Minimal, Minimalistic, Blue, black.
